{"tid":1986568,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧：美國或不會恢復資助世衛　研究另一機構取代","createTime":"2020-04-24T02:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T14:47:40.000Z","uid":28114,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"06d7f2cbaa5bafb196dce6f97fabfa4ba312697d","tid":1986568,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/MIKE_X49UE_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FMIKE_X49UE_1200x0.png&h=3b08d14a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧表示，除非世衛進行徹底改革，否則美國可能不會恢復資助世界衛生組織。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧繼於當地星期四（23日）的記者會上嚴詞指摘中共隱瞞疫情、世衛未有按規定要求中國呈報疫症數據後，晚上接受 Fox News 訪問時說，世衛必須進行結構性改革。被問到是否要求世衛換領導人時，蓬佩奧說，必須比換人做得更徹底，否則「美國可能不再恢復資助，不再讓美國納稅人的錢協助世衛。」<br />\n<br />\n他在同日出席一個電台節目時，被問到會否考慮由另一個機構取代世衛的角色，蓬佩奧：「這正正是我們要研究的事。」他說，如果世衛是盡責做到其功能，美國一定會支持，但如果其工作不符預期，美國會在國際間尋求其他合作夥伴，務求提供一個能符合預期、有管理的架構。<br />\n<br />\n中國昨日宣布向世衛額外捐助 3,000 萬美元。<br />\n<br />\nReuters／CNA<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3/?fbclid=IwAR1WMCaxAAxmAdAkoAdZEEm8Si7-A217vrAYGeuVVmSy6mb3495X2EY2xZ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2581%25A2%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%258A%25A9%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E5%258F%25A6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E5%258F%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1WMCaxAAxmAdAkoAdZEEm8Si7-A217vrAYGeuVVmSy6mb3495X2EY2xZ8&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hXwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=ec57cef5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3